# 🔴 Hotstuff Copy Trading Bot

> Automated copy trading bot for [Hotstuff.trade](https://app.hotstuff.trade/join/hot) — follows top traders and mirrors their positions in real time.

```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  Auto-follow top traders  │  Real-time sync  │  24/7  ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
```

---

## How It Works

The bot monitors selected trader wallets on Hotstuff.trade and automatically mirrors their trades:

```
  Target trader opens BTC-PERP LONG $500
          │
          ▼
  Bot detects position change via REST polling
          │
          ▼
  Bot opens BTC-PERP LONG (scaled to your wallet size)
          │
          ▼
  Target trader closes → Bot closes automatically ✅
```

**Position scaling** adjusts trade size relative to your wallet:

```
  Target wallet:  $10,000   opens $1,000 (10%)
  Your wallet:    $300      bot opens $30 (10%) ✅
```

---

## Features

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| ✅ Real-time copy | Polls target wallet every 5s for position changes |
| ✅ Position scaling | Mirrors trades proportionally to your wallet size |
| ✅ Multi-target | Follow multiple wallets simultaneously |
| ✅ Risk limits | Daily loss limit, max position, unrealized stop |
| ✅ Telegram alerts | Trade notifications, hourly reports, halt alerts |
| ✅ Auto close | Closes all positions on halt or stop signal |
| ✅ Startup sync | Syncs current positions before first trade |

---

## Quickstart

### 1. Clone & install

```bash
git clone https://github.com/omgmad/hotstuff-copy-trading-bot
cd hotstuff-copy-trading-bot
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Setup agent wallet

On Hotstuff: **Settings → API → Create Agent Wallet**

Copy the agent wallet address and private key.

### 3. Configure `.env`

```bash
cp .env.example .env
nano .env
```

```env
PRIVATE_KEY=0x_your_agent_wallet_private_key
WALLET_ADDRESS=0x_your_agent_wallet_address

# Wallet(s) to copy — comma separated
TARGET_WALLETS=0xABC123...,0xDEF456...

# Optional — Telegram alerts
TELEGRAM_TOKEN=1234567890:ABCdef...
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=123456789
```

### 4. Run

```bash
python3 hotstuff_copy_bot.py
```

```
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║   🔴  HOTSTUFF Copy Trading Bot                      ║
║   ⚠️  Real money on mainnet. Start small!             ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

Confirm to start [yes/no]: yes
🚀 Copy trading started...
```

### 5. Run 24/7 with screen (VPS)

```bash
# Start in background
screen -S copybot
source venv/bin/activate
python3 hotstuff_copy_bot.py

# Detach — bot keeps running
Ctrl+A, then D

# Reattach later
screen -r copybot
```

---

## Configuration

```python
# hotstuff_copy_bot.py — CONFIG section

"target_wallets":          ["0xABC...", "0xDEF..."],  # wallets to copy
"copy_ratio":              1.0,    # 1.0 = mirror exact %, 0.5 = half size
"order_size_usd":          100,    # $ per copied trade
"max_position_usd":        300,    # max per symbol
"max_total_exposure_usd":  900,    # total across all symbols
"daily_loss_limit_usd":    6.0,    # halt threshold (5% of $120 wallet)
"unrealized_loss_limit_usd": 8.0,  # force-close threshold
"consecutive_loss_limit":  5,      # circuit breaker trigger
"circuit_breaker_pause_sec": 900,  # 15 min pause after trigger
"refresh_interval":        5,      # polling interval (seconds)
"symbols": ["BTC-PERP", "ETH-PERP", "SOL-PERP", "HYPE-PERP"],
```

---

## Risk Management

```
Daily loss limit hit ────────────► HALT + close all positions
                                         │
Unrealized < -$8 ────────────────► market close all
                                         │
5 consecutive losses ────────────► 15 min pause (circuit breaker)
                                         │
Total exposure > $900 ───────────► block new trades
                                         │
Per-symbol position > $300 ──────► block that symbol
```

All halt events send Telegram alert with full status and next steps.

---

## Telegram Commands

| Command | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `/status` | Current positions, P&L, daily stats |
| `/pause` | Stop copying new trades |
| `/resume` | Resume copying |
| `/close` | Close all positions (market order) |
| `/stop` | Stop bot completely |
| `/help` | Show all commands |

